How I Create My Beachy Waves 💫

Important things to remember: 

✨ Wave your hair away from your face 
✨ Leave the very ends out so they are still straight 
✨ Run your hands through your hair a lot once you’re finished to make the waves nice and loose. If your hair drops quite easily maybe not so much. 

I don’t use any finishing products in my hair as it holds really well but this is personal choice.
